headline: KDP strikes distribution deal for Cove Soda in Canada
summary: Jean Gagnon, vice-president of cold beverages at KDP Canada, said the alliance is a “bold and strategic step forward in the evolution of our CSD portfolio”.

headline: If Pepsi Wants to Win, It Has to Play Coke’s Game
summary: Coke shed bottling and poured money into marketing. Unless Pepsi slims down, the gap between the two will continue to widen.
